text: Elektra is a 2005 American superhero movie directed by Rob Bowman. It was based on the Marvel character Elektra by Frank Miller. Elektra's main actors are Jennifer Garner, Goran Višnjić and Will Yun Lee. == References == Category:2005 movies Category:English-language movies Category:2000s superhero movies Category:Daredevil (movie series) Category:Film noir Category:Movies produced by Avi Arad Category:Movies set in Japan Category:Movie spin-offs Category:20th Century Fox movies Category:Screenplays by Zak Penn Category:American superhero movies
